beer_name: Monday Night Blood Orange Blind Pirate

review_blob:
Bottle to glass, pours black. Taste is sweet. Medium body, light carbonation, creamy mouth feel. Finishes sweet, just slightly bitter. notes of chocolate, coffee, easy drinking stout.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

So far in my limited experience this is the best IPA I've had. It's just another example of Monday Night making great beer.
